query:
INSERT INTO panes (id, session_id, tmux_pane, pane_type, created_at)
            VALUES (?1, ?2, ?3, ?4, ?5)
            RETURNING 
                id as "id!: String",
                session_id as "session_id!: String",
                tmux_pane as "tmux_pane?: String",
                pane_type as "pane_type!: String",
                content as "content?: String",
                metadata as "metadata?: String",
                created_at as "created_at!: NaiveDateTime"
